      "width": 476,
      "height": 182,
      "text": "embed-url\n  user_token + form_id + output_project\n\nworkflow/sync\n  query  -> 读取 models / opinions / attachments\n  active -> SJ 送审\n  agree  -> 同意并推进到下一节点\n  return -> 驳回并回写原因\n  stop   -> 终止流程",
